### 1. Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userN": "john_doe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Login WITHOUT Remember Me
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userN": "john_doe",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": false
}

### 3. Login WITH Remember Me (issues refresh token cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userN": "john_doe",
  "password": "password123",
  "rememberMe": true
}

### 4. Refresh access token (uses httpOnly cookie automatically)
POST {{baseUrl}}/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

### 5. Get basket (paste accessToken from login response above into @accessToken)
GET {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 6. Add item to basket
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "product_001",
  "name": "Wireless Headphones",
  "price": 59.99,
  "quantity": 1
}

### 7. Add another item
POST {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "product_002",
  "name": "Mechanical Keyboard",
  "price": 89.99,
  "quantity": 2
}

### 8. Update item quantity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket/product_001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### 9. Remove one item from basket
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket/product_001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 10. Clear entire basket
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/{{userId}}/basket
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 11. Logout (clears refresh token cookie + invalidates server-side)
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Content-Type: application/json